    "description": "这是一款快节奏的俯视角射击与塔防游戏。你需要改造并升级你的战车，建造防御建筑以保护你的基地，探索这个世界并摧毁所有敌人！不要忘了在敌人进攻时回来防守！你能坚持到最后吗？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/30abab684a33ba73e5c642b5ba2acb0c.poster.avif?t=1679761271\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/30abab684a33ba73e5c642b5ba2acb0c.webm?t=1679761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/30abab684a33ba73e5c642b5ba2acb0c.mp4?t=1679761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>掌握战车操作，击毁一切敌人。探索各种各样的战车模块组合，不同的敌人具有不同的攻击方式，更加强大的敌人意味着更丰厚的回报。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/3ed6ef530c5bbde85f30a3865b6adf89.poster.avif?t=1679761271\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/3ed6ef530c5bbde85f30a3865b6adf89.webm?t=1679761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/3ed6ef530c5bbde85f30a3865b6adf89.mp4?t=1679761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每一个被击毁的敌人都会掉落有用的组件，将它们带回基地以升级自身。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/5c8aebbdb9185011c28aaf9ee66e959a.poster.avif?t=1679761271\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/5c8aebbdb9185011c28aaf9ee66e959a.webm?t=1679761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/5c8aebbdb9185011c28aaf9ee66e959a.mp4?t=1679761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索各种各样的战车模块组合。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >防守</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/ea56a011ea615f8d6bca3913c9acb95d.poster.avif?t=1679761271\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/ea56a011ea615f8d6bca3913c9acb95d.webm?t=1679761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214260/extras/ea56a011ea615f8d6bca3913c9acb95d.mp4?t=1679761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>敌人们不会坐以待毙，随着时间的推移，你会遭受越来越强大的敌人的攻击。你可以建造多样的防御建筑以防御敌人的进攻。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索</h2>建造加速道路和传送门去更远的地方猎杀敌人，摧毁他们的基地，并带回战利品。权衡探索和回防的时间，一定不要忘了，在敌人进攻之前回来防守。<br><br><br><br><br>-----------------------------<br>本游戏是单人独立开发，我正在寻找志同道合的2D美术以共同开发未来的作品，对自己的美术能力有信心的话，欢迎联系我QQ: 2403353662",
